<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10092522>
    dc:description "Figure 5. a–i, Phryganoporus candidus. a–c, Townsville, Qld, female: a, body, dorsal; b, body, ventral; c, epigynum. d,e, Grenfell, NSW, male palp: d, ventral; e, prolateral. f, Mellin Jerrie Well, WA, female: internal genitalia. g–i, Black Mountain,ACT: g, male palp, retrolateral tibia & patella; h,i, female: h, epigynum; i, internal genitalia. j–l, Phryganoporus vandiemeni, Wilson’s Promontory, Vic.: j,k, female: j, epigynum; k, internal genitalia. l, male palp, retrolateral. Scale lines: a, b: 1 mm; others 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10092522/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

